Tamasin Ramsay https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamasin_Ramsay 0 Tamasin Ramsay (born 1969) is an Australian anthropologist (with a background as an actress), having studied medical anthropology at the University of Melbourne and received her PhD in the same field from Monash University in 2009. Tamasin resides in Melbourne, Australia.
